article.description: — Calvin Wishart had a career-high 23 points as UC Santa Barbara topped Pepperdine 86-74 on Friday night.
article.headline: Wishart lifts UC Santa Barbara past Pepperdine 86-74
article.linkText: Wishart lifts UC Santa Barbara past Pepperdine 86-74
article.story: SANTA BARBARA, Calif. -- — Calvin Wishart had a career-high 23 points as UC Santa Barbara topped Pepperdine 86-74 on Friday night. Miles Norris had 13 points and nine rebounds for UC Santa Barbara (4-2). Ajare Sanni added 12 points. Amadou Sow had 11 points and nine rebounds. Jan Zidek tied a season high with 20 points and had seven rebounds for the Waves (2-8), whose losing streak reached six games. Victor Ohia Obioha added 15 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
